snippet.textDisplay:
I know you probably won’t see this but if you do just know that all this hate your getting dumped on you is just stupid. I didn’t understand why your other video was so disliked. I think people are having far too high expectations for you, but just know that you are not living your life just to make other people happy. I know it’s really hard to fully believe that, especially since your on youtube, but you were not put on this earth to meet others expectations for you. It is so unfair for people to hold you to this preconceived version of you in their minds, because that is not what you should be striving to be. Everyone saying things like “you’ve changed” yeah obviously you have. We all do it’s a part of life and growing. We are not supposed to be the same people our entire lives. Who gives a literal crap if you dyed a streak in your hair?? There is so much stuff to be genuinely worrying about in our world right now, and coming after a young person on the internet who is not hurting anyone, saying harmful things or just being a bad person is not one of them, so why are we making such a big fuss??

Keep being you, Emma, and if you do need to take a break from all this, please don’t feel obligated to keep posting. Love you❤️

I know it’s really hard to fully believe that, especially since your on youtube, but *you were not put on this earth to meet others expectations for you.* It is so unfair for people to hold you to this preconceived version of you in their minds, because that is not what you should be striving to be. Everyone saying things like “you’ve changed” yeah obviously you have. We all do it’s a part of life and growing.   We are not supposed to be the same people our entire lives. Who gives a literal crap if you dyed a streak in your hair?? There is so much stuff to be genuinely worrying about in our world right now, and coming after a young person on the internet who is not hurting anyone, saying harmful things or just being a bad person is not one of them, so why are we making such a big fuss??

Keep being you, Emma, and if you do need to take a break from all this, please don’t feel obligated to keep posting. Love you❤️
